{"id":645657,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/05/【立此存照】坦克世界玩家因真名李鹏无/","date":"2020-05-28T06:44:54Z","modified":"2020-05-28T06:46:12Z","title":"【立此存照】“坦克世界”玩家因真名“李鹏”无法实名认证","content":"<p>近日，有网络游戏“坦克世界”玩家在贴吧爆料称，自己因真名“李鹏”而无法通过360账号转移要求的“实名认证”，官方客服建议是“把鹏字换一个谐音字试一下”。这位玩家或因无法理解一款坦克游戏为何对“李鹏”这一名字如此敏感而异常愤怒，宣布拒玩游戏。</p>\n<p>目前，该帖原帖已被<a href=\"http://tieba.baidu.com/p/6707725941\">删除</a>。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/photo_2020-05-28_14-26-07.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-645659\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/photo_2020-05-28_14-26-07.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"1037\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/photo_2020-05-28_14-26-07.jpg 679w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/photo_2020-05-28_14-26-07-159x300.jpg 159w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/photo_2020-05-28_14-26-07-543x1024.jpg 543w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/photo_2020-05-28_14-26-29.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-645660\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/photo_2020-05-28_14-26-29.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"319\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/photo_2020-05-28_14-26-29.jpg 801w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/photo_2020-05-28_14-26-29-300x174.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/photo_2020-05-28_14-26-29-768x446.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/photo_2020-05-28_14-27-05.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-645663\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/photo_2020-05-28_14-27-05.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"778\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/photo_2020-05-28_14-27-05.jpg 540w, https: